data.description: Brand new flooring!! Welcome to this nice family home located on a corner lot in the Mesa school district. This home features 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 full baths, ensuring plenty of space and privacy for your loved ones! Enjoy creating unforgettable memories in the cozy living room with a fireplace, perfect for chilly evenings. Lots of natural lighting throughout the home, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Host friends and family in the private backyard, complete with a spacious covered patio. Reach out today for a private showing- Summer @ 850-376-4659
